author: Sam Sutton
title: Murphy: New Jersey will ‘stay the course’ on social distancing
description: He reiterated that he believes stay-at-home orders are necessary in the context of global pandemic’s course across New Jersey.
content:
Gov. Phil Murphy. | Seth Wenig/AP Photo
New Jersey Gov. Phil Murphy said Tuesday he has no intention of reversing any of the steps hes taken over the last three weeks to mitigate the spread of the coronavirus.
